If vireblc(LIGNE,2)<>vireblc(format$("K:3c",[F:CAL]DIE(1)),2)
 Call TRACE2(-2,"Error formato DIE K:3c"-num$(LIGNE),2) From SUBIMPOBJ
Endif
[F:CAL]DIE(1) = vireblc(format$("K:3c",[F:CAL]DIE(1)),1)
LIGNE = VALIMP(3)
 # Alphanumérique: CCE(0)
[F:CAL]CCE(0) = vireblc(LIGNE,2)
LIGNE = VALIMP(4)
 # Alphanumérique: CCE(1)
[F:CAL]CCE(1) = vireblc(LIGNE,2)
ACTION='AP_IMPORT' : Gosub ACTION From SUBIMPOBJ
Return

